===Alternative forms===
* {{l|el|Ελλάς|tr=Ellás|g=f}}

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc|el}} {{term|Ἑλλάδα||tr=Hellada|lang=grc}}, accusative form of {{term|Ἑλλάς||Greece|tr=Hellas|lang=grc}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/eˈlaða/|lang=el}}, {{X-SAMPA|/e"laDa/|lang=el}}

===Proper noun===
{{el-noun-proper|f|Elláda}}
# [[Greece]]

====Usage notes====
{{l|el|Ελλάς|tr=Ellás}} is the former, [[Katharevousa]], word for what in Standard Modern Greek is now called {{l|el|Ελλάδα|tr=Elláda}} or {{l|el|Ελληνική Δημοκρατία|tr=Ellinikí Dimokratía}}, the official name.

